420109,101,807,28,46,1,94,14,"‘‘ na heva kho aṭṭha vimokkhe kāyena phusitvā viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā parikkhīṇā honti. "
420110,101,807,47,54,1,36,5,Ayaṃ vuccati puggalo paññāvimutto’’ ti. 
