424816,102,759,85,91,1,39,5,Kaṅkhāyeva hi kaṅkhāṭhāniyā dhammā nāma. 
424817,102,759,92,98,1,42,6,Tattha ekaṃ kaṅkhampi na nīharantīti attho. 
424818,102,759,99,109,1,91,10,So evaṃ bahussutatitthaṃ anupasaṅkamitvā sakaṅkho kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vaḍḍhetuṃ na sakkoti. 
424819,102,759,110,124,1,82,13,"Yathā vā so gopālako titthaṃ na jānāti, evaṃ ayampi bhikkhu dhammatitthaṃ na jānāti. "
424820,102,759,125,139,1,141,12,"Ajānanto avisaye pañhaṃ pucchati, ābhidhammikaṃ upasaṅkamitvā kappiyākappiyaṃ pucchati, vinayadharaṃ upasaṅkamitvā rūpārūpaparicchedaṃ pucchati. "
424821,102,759,140,146,1,38,6,Te avisaye puṭṭhā kathetuṃ na sakkonti. 
424822,102,759,147,160,1,79,11,So attanā sakaṅkho kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vaḍḍhetuṃ na sakkoti… pe… paribāhiro hoti. 
424823,102,760,2,21,1,107,16,"Na pītaṃ {jānātī}ti yathā so gopālako pītāpītaṃ na jānāti, evaṃ dhammūpasañhitaṃ pāmojjaṃ na jānāti na labhati. "
424824,102,760,22,43,1,155,17,"Savanamayaṃ puññakiriyavatthuṃ nissāya ānisaṃsaṃ na vindati, dhammassavanaggaṃ gantvā sakkaccaṃ na suṇāti, nisinno niddāyati, kathaṃ katheti, aññavihitako hoti. "
424825,102,760,44,58,1,91,12,So sakkaccaṃ dhammaṃ assuṇanto kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vaḍḍhetuṃ na sakkoti… pe… paribāhiro hoti. 
424826,102,761,2,25,1,127,17,"Na vīthiṃ {jānātī}ti so gopālako maggāmaggaṃ viya‘‘ ayaṃ lokiyo, ayaṃ lokuttaro’’ ti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
424827,102,761,26,38,1,87,10,Ajānanto lokiyamagge abhinivisitvā lokuttaraṃ nibbattetuṃ na sakkoti… pe… paribāhiro hoti. 
424828,102,762,2,24,1,135,16,"Na gocarakusalo {hotī}ti so gopālako pañcāhikasattāhikacāre viya cattāro satipaṭṭhāne‘‘ ime lokiyā, ime lokuttarā’’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
