428928,103,891,2,2,1,12,1,Santosakathā 
428929,103,892,2,19,1,94,9,"215. Idha, mahārāja, bhikkhu santuṭṭho {hotī}ti ettha {santuṭṭho}ti itarītarapaccayasantosena samannāgato. "
428930,103,892,20,35,1,119,11,"So panesa santoso dvādasavidho hoti, seyyathidaṃ– cīvare yathālābhasantoso, yathābalasantoso, yathāsāruppasantosoti tividho. "
428931,103,892,36,38,1,18,2,Evaṃ piṇḍapātādīsu. 
428932,103,892,39,41,1,23,2,Tassāyaṃ pabhedavaṇṇanā– 
428933,103,893,2,11,1,53,8,"Idha bhikkhu cīvaraṃ labhati, sundaraṃ vā asundaraṃ vā. "
428934,103,893,12,23,1,56,9,"So teneva yāpeti, aññaṃ na pattheti, labhantopi na gaṇhati. "
428935,103,893,24,27,1,33,3,Ayamassa cīvare yathālābhasantoso. 
428936,103,893,28,41,1,84,10,"Atha pana pakatidubbalo vā hoti, ābādhajarābhibhūto vā, garucīvaraṃ pārupanto kilamati. "
428937,103,893,42,52,1,83,10,So sabhāgena bhikkhunā saddhiṃ taṃ parivattetvā lahukena yāpentopi santuṭṭhova hoti. 
428938,103,893,53,56,1,32,3,Ayamassa cīvare yathābalasantoso. 
428939,103,893,57,60,1,29,3,Aparo paṇītapaccayalābhī hoti. 
428940,103,893,61,99,1,311,35,"So pattacīvarādīnaṃ aññataraṃ mahagghapattacīvaraṃ bahūni vā pana pattacīvarāni labhitvā idaṃ therānaṃ cirapabbajitānaṃ, idaṃ bahussutānaṃ anurūpaṃ, idaṃ gilānānaṃ, idaṃ appalābhīnaṃ hotūti datvā tesaṃ purāṇacīvaraṃ vā gahetvā saṅkārakūṭādito vā nantakāni uccinitvā tehi saṅghāṭiṃ katvā dhārentopi santuṭṭhova hoti. "
